HEADWORD: Ziphiidae
<hw>Zi*phi"i*dae</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A natural
family of cetaceans comprising the beaked whales; in some esp. former
classifications included in the family
<fam>Physeteridae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Ziphiidae</fam>, Hyperodontidae, family
<fam>Hyperodontidae</fam>.</syn>⟦br⟧
